« La Semeuse »
Le passé de Rillieux la pape est Évoqué dans cette grande fresque. Ancien champs de culture de choux. Aujourd’hui devenu un quartier très populaire de la banlieue de Lyon, nous devions rendre cet hommage sous une composition de style art nouveau. Dédié aux résidents de ces quartiers Unique… Respect ✊.

Style learning! Jamin’ with  @tonesrock in chi phat community. Thanks to @fonkiworld, @muralsforcambodia, @de_forest_nature_escape and @wildlife_alliance to make it possible. Life time memories here!

Legendary @zek156 , a true pioneer of Montreal Canada's graffiti & mural scene is in Asia for the first time! 🎨🌟 With his razor-sharp line work, attention to detail, and vibrant color combinations, Zek's art is a sight to behold. His dedication has earned him the respect of his peers and community, and his figurative work and large-scale productions can be found throughout the globe. Come find his latest masterpiece he did in his first trip to Cambodia at @factory_phnompenh !
